      About this item

      • Flawless 2K Clarity with 145 FOV: N1 wireless cameras for home security captures more of your surroundings with ultra-wide 145 lens and delivers crisp 2K HD videos with vivid details both day and night. With Color Night Vision and 8X Digital Zoom, you'll never miss a thing even far from 6m and receive instant alerts of anything suspicious.
      • No Monthly Fees and 16TB Expandable Local Storage: Feel secure knowing there are no subscription fees. Our H1 HomeStation boasts 16GB of eMMC storage, expandable to 16TB(*Note: Hard Drive Not Included), which can cover your lifetime storage needs. Rest assured, your privacy is guaranteed with TV Rheinland certifications. Plus, AES+RSA encryption safeguards your data, ensuring it's accessible only to you.
      • 210-Day Battery Life with IP67: Our powerful 7,800mAh battery provides an extraordinary 210 days of crystal-clear surveillance on a single charge. Even in extreme temperatures ranging from -4F to 122F, our IP67-rated outdoor security camera offers long-term peace of mind with minimal maintenance. *NOTE: 210-Day Battery life is based on lab data with 10 seconds of video per recording, 30 recordings per day. Our wireless security cameras are best suited for outdoor use because battery life varies with the frequency of events and recording length.
      • Instant Alert & Flexible Installation: Stay updated with human tracking, offering quick notifications and snapshots when anyone approaches, lingers, or passes by your home, quickly responding to security issues. With its wire-free design, you can easily set our wireless security camera up anywhere in minutes.*NOTE: To ensure full functionality of your security camera, please download the "baseus Security" app.
      • 2-Year Warranty & Lifetime Tech Support: Find comfort in our 2-year warranty, securing your investment. Our lifelong technical support ensures any queries are promptly resolved, offering continuous assistance throughout your product's lifetime. *Whats More, Our HomeStation supports up to 8 cameras to connect. With N1 add on cameras, you can build a better home security system.
      • *Note: The N1 2-Cam Kit does not support 24/7 continuous recording. It is battery powered and strikes a good balance between battery life and event capture. It records only when the camera captures moving objects.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
